1
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,509
♪The world keeps changing♪

2
00:00:17,510 --> 00:00:19,979
♪A thousand years pass
in the blink of an eye♪

3
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,159
♪Shoulder to shoulder♪

4
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:24,399
♪We stand above the world♪

5
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,590
♪Our identities switch♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:29,320
♪The world turns upside down♪

7
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,729
♪Watch me♪

8
00:00:31,730 --> 00:00:35,319
♪Stir up a storm♪

9
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,609
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

10
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:40,059
♪Our blood is boiling♪

11
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:45,289
♪The genius emperor plots
with brilliant strategy♪

12
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:49,709
♪The slacker general
is unmatched in battle♪

13
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,199
♪The business world is in turmoil♪

14
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,749
♪The court is rife with intrigue♪

15
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:59,169
♪We will conquer the world♪

16
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:03,510
♪There's no escape for the traitors♪

17
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:07,999
=No Way! My Bro is the Emperor=

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,160
=Episode 16=

19
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:14,040
(Xiaoyao Pavilion)

20
00:01:19,770 --> 00:01:21,860
Why are you looking for Fushou Cream
at Xiaoyao Pavilion?

21
00:01:22,660 --> 00:01:24,459
I don't know anything.

22
00:01:24,460 --> 00:01:26,140
Under the Jing law,

23
00:01:26,570 --> 00:01:29,170
selling Fushou Cream is punishable
by exile to the northern frontier.

24
00:01:30,210 --> 00:01:31,090
Besides,

25
00:01:31,330 --> 00:01:32,810
you're using drugs.

26
00:01:33,210 --> 00:01:35,220
Didn't you think about your family?

27
00:01:36,580 --> 00:01:37,730
My family?

28
00:01:38,490 --> 00:01:39,340
Enough.

29
00:01:39,610 --> 00:01:41,570
Quit giving a lecture
to someone like him.

30
00:01:46,900 --> 00:01:49,010
If you know what's good for you,

31
00:01:49,300 --> 00:01:51,780
you'd better confess now.

32
00:01:52,460 --> 00:01:54,370
I told you, I know nothing.

33
00:01:55,100 --> 00:01:56,620
What right do you have to arrest me?

34
00:01:57,050 --> 00:01:58,019
Let me out!

35
00:01:58,020 --> 00:01:58,900
Someone!

36
00:01:59,460 --> 00:02:00,620
Help!

37
00:02:01,580 --> 00:02:03,220
Tough nut, aren't you?

38
00:02:03,970 --> 00:02:05,730
Proceed to the final step.

39
00:02:10,980 --> 00:02:11,899
What are you doing?

40
00:02:11,900 --> 00:02:13,580
Easy there, tough guy.

41
00:02:13,980 --> 00:02:15,460
We're just checking your condition.

42
00:02:15,930 --> 00:02:16,830
Go.

43
00:02:17,020 --> 00:02:18,090
Let me out!

44
00:02:18,330 --> 00:02:19,259
Let me out!

45
00:02:19,260 --> 00:02:20,130
Let me out!

46
00:02:20,330 --> 00:02:21,460
What are you doing?

47
00:02:22,330 --> 00:02:23,620
What are you doing?

48
00:02:29,740 --> 00:02:30,699
You're so weak,

49
00:02:30,700 --> 00:02:31,810
and you're still doing drugs?

50
00:02:32,650 --> 00:02:34,740
I don't know anything.

51
00:02:34,770 --> 00:02:35,370
More.

52
00:02:39,770 --> 00:02:40,460
More.

53
00:02:42,610 --> 00:02:43,859
I'll talk!

54
00:02:43,860 --> 00:02:45,620
I'll talk!

55
00:02:46,020 --> 00:02:47,410
I'll tell you everything.

56
00:02:48,140 --> 00:02:48,950
Well.

57
00:02:49,020 --> 00:02:52,049
People in the capital
are selling the Fushou Cream.

58
00:02:52,050 --> 00:02:52,930
How?

59
00:02:53,460 --> 00:02:54,899
They pack the Fushou Cream

60
00:02:54,900 --> 00:02:58,180
inside Xiaoyao Cream boxes.

61
00:02:58,300 --> 00:03:00,340
It looks just like face cream.

62
00:03:00,420 --> 00:03:01,930
Where's your supplier?

63
00:03:02,980 --> 00:03:05,340
How would I know?

64
00:03:05,530 --> 00:03:08,020
Put me down!

65
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:21,410
We shut down Zuixian House,

66
00:03:22,490 --> 00:03:24,850
yet Fushou Cream is everywhere
in the capital.

67
00:03:26,810 --> 00:03:28,620
They switched from wholesale
to street sales.

68
00:03:28,770 --> 00:03:30,090
That makes them harder to catch.

69
00:03:30,260 --> 00:03:31,810
Taking them on one by one won't be easy.

70
00:03:32,770 --> 00:03:34,090
But we can

71
00:03:34,770 --> 00:03:36,250
catch them all at once.

72
00:03:37,420 --> 00:03:38,460
How?

73
00:03:38,580 --> 00:03:40,900
We'll make good use of Xiaoyao Pavilion.

74
00:03:41,530 --> 00:03:42,580
Let's set a trap.

75
00:03:43,330 --> 00:03:44,930
A sting operation.

76
00:03:47,610 --> 00:03:49,900
Could you be a little more specific?

77
00:03:50,370 --> 00:03:51,340
Well...

78
00:03:51,980 --> 00:03:53,180
Before...

79
00:03:53,580 --> 00:03:54,130
No.

80
00:03:54,700 --> 00:03:55,620
Didn't they use

81
00:03:55,980 --> 00:03:56,579
Xiaoyao Cream

82
00:03:56,580 --> 00:03:58,699
as a front to sell drugs?

83
00:03:58,700 --> 00:03:59,740
Now that

84
00:04:00,460 --> 00:04:01,459
you've stopped wholesale,

85
00:04:01,460 --> 00:04:02,850
they're bound to panic.

86
00:04:02,860 --> 00:04:03,810
So

87
00:04:03,860 --> 00:04:06,410
you want me to resume wholesale?

88
00:04:06,460 --> 00:04:07,220
Exactly.

89
00:04:07,610 --> 00:04:08,930
Not only that,

90
00:04:09,020 --> 00:04:10,530
we're going all out.

91
00:04:10,930 --> 00:04:12,620
We'll hold a huge sale.

92
00:04:12,650 --> 00:04:14,220
The more you buy, the more you save.

93
00:04:14,700 --> 00:04:15,720
That way,

94
00:04:15,740 --> 00:04:18,260
we can secretly watch the bulk buyers.

95
00:04:18,650 --> 00:04:21,050
We'll follow the trail

96
00:04:21,140 --> 00:04:21,940
and find

97
00:04:22,410 --> 00:04:23,850
who's behind the drug trade.

98
00:04:26,170 --> 00:04:29,020
Business at Xiaoyao Pavilion
has been great lately.

99
00:04:29,460 --> 00:04:30,699
But

100
00:04:30,700 --> 00:04:32,290
most of our customers are women.

101
00:04:33,410 --> 00:04:36,140
If we're throwing a huge sale,

102
00:04:36,580 --> 00:04:38,710
I'm afraid

103
00:04:39,090 --> 00:04:40,260
it won't draw enough attention.

104
00:04:40,330 --> 00:04:41,969
Xiao Ling

105
00:04:41,970 --> 00:04:45,090
managed to bring this place
back from the brink.

106
00:04:45,970 --> 00:04:47,940
As her brother

107
00:04:48,620 --> 00:04:50,290
and the Emperor,

108
00:04:51,380 --> 00:04:52,260
this time,

109
00:04:53,330 --> 00:04:54,340
I'll be

110
00:04:54,730 --> 00:04:57,530
your spokesperson.

111
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,939
(The Best Pavilion in the World)

112
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:05,700
Bold, powerful strokes.

113
00:05:06,090 --> 00:05:07,409
A remarkable piece of calligraphy.

114
00:05:07,410 --> 00:05:08,290
Eunuch Xu,

115
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:11,340
have this plaque beautifully mounted.

116
00:05:11,530 --> 00:05:12,850
Yes, Your Majesty.

117
00:05:13,940 --> 00:05:14,900
My ministers,

118
00:05:15,330 --> 00:05:17,730
tomorrow marks Xiaoyao Pavilion's
first anniversary.

119
00:05:18,150 --> 00:05:19,649
Why don't you join me

120
00:05:19,650 --> 00:05:22,450
in presenting this plaque

121
00:05:22,530 --> 00:05:24,089
to General Gu?

122
00:05:24,090 --> 00:05:24,940
What do you think?

123
00:05:25,730 --> 00:05:26,460
Your Majesty,

124
00:05:26,530 --> 00:05:28,490
though Official Gu is your trusted aide,

125
00:05:28,500 --> 00:05:30,699
Xiaoyao Pavilion is still private property.

126
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:33,140
I'm afraid it may invite criticism.

127
00:05:34,170 --> 00:05:35,820
Chancellor Hu, I disagree.

128
00:05:36,580 --> 00:05:38,019
Though privately owned,

129
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:40,490
much of its profits go to the treasury.

130
00:05:40,700 --> 00:05:43,170
It has contributed greatly to Jing.

131
00:05:43,500 --> 00:05:44,650
You're right, Your Majesty.

132
00:05:45,090 --> 00:05:47,850
Not only should we go,
but we should also invite more people.

133
00:05:48,260 --> 00:05:51,380
Summon the ministers from the Ministries
of Works, Justice, and Personnel.

134
00:05:51,650 --> 00:05:52,970
They'll all come with us.

135
00:05:53,260 --> 00:05:54,850
I obey, Your Majesty.

136
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,360
(The Best Pavilion in the World)

137
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,950
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

138
00:06:05,530 --> 00:06:07,699
Thank you, Your Majesty, for this honor.

139
00:06:07,700 --> 00:06:09,019
To celebrate our anniversary,

140
00:06:09,020 --> 00:06:10,899
everything is buy one, get one free.

141
00:06:10,900 --> 00:06:12,650
And all services are half price.

142
00:06:12,850 --> 00:06:14,499
Enjoy yourselves,

143
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:15,730
and happy shopping!

144
00:06:16,020 --> 00:06:17,380
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

145
00:06:19,170 --> 00:06:21,059
- Everything's half price today!
- Your Majesty.

146
00:06:21,060 --> 00:06:21,649
Follow me.

147
00:06:21,650 --> 00:06:23,900
Free samples here!

148
00:06:25,140 --> 00:06:25,619
Come on.

149
00:06:25,620 --> 00:06:26,289
Today,

150
00:06:26,290 --> 00:06:28,400
everything is half price.

151
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:31,320
The Snow Cream  smells wonderful
with just one dab. You'll look years younger.

152
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:32,019
Come get yours.

153
00:06:32,020 --> 00:06:32,409
Come!

154
00:06:32,410 --> 00:06:34,530
Take a look at our Snow Cream.

155
00:06:34,730 --> 00:06:36,480
- Look at the texture.
- We have gift sets too!

156
00:06:38,900 --> 00:06:40,260
Greetings, Your Majesty.

157
00:06:40,820 --> 00:06:41,900
We're outside the palace.

158
00:06:41,970 --> 00:06:43,700
Let's leave rank behind.
We're all guests here.

159
00:06:44,330 --> 00:06:45,460
No need for formalities.

160
00:06:45,620 --> 00:06:46,580
Just enjoy yourselves.

161
00:06:52,210 --> 00:06:55,090
Please spare my brother.

162
00:06:55,530 --> 00:06:57,140
That's easy.

163
00:06:57,820 --> 00:06:59,940
Just do as you're told,

164
00:07:00,060 --> 00:07:02,050
and he'll be safe.

165
00:07:03,140 --> 00:07:04,410
Kill Gu Bei.

166
00:07:04,970 --> 00:07:06,220
Then you and your brother

167
00:07:06,500 --> 00:07:07,820
will both be free.

168
00:07:12,850 --> 00:07:13,730
What?

169
00:07:14,140 --> 00:07:15,260
Can't do it?

170
00:07:16,850 --> 00:07:18,220
You've fallen for him?

171
00:07:19,060 --> 00:07:20,260
I

172
00:07:21,730 --> 00:07:23,220
will carry out the mission.

173
00:07:27,290 --> 00:07:28,170
Official Gu,

174
00:07:28,210 --> 00:07:29,379
congratulations.

175
00:07:29,380 --> 00:07:31,849
May Xiaoyao Pavilion prosper

176
00:07:31,850 --> 00:07:33,380
throughout Jing.

177
00:07:34,580 --> 00:07:35,529
Thank you, Chancellor Hu.

178
00:07:35,530 --> 00:07:36,729
Your private room is ready.

179
00:07:36,730 --> 00:07:37,490
This way, please.

180
00:07:39,170 --> 00:07:40,059
Congratulations!

181
00:07:40,060 --> 00:07:41,560
- Congratulations!
- Thank you. Please.

182
00:07:45,620 --> 00:07:46,529
Well?

183
00:07:46,530 --> 00:07:47,530
Did you notice anything?

184
00:07:49,060 --> 00:07:51,170
I thought I saw Yan Qiu.

185
00:07:52,410 --> 00:07:53,050
Are you sure?

186
00:07:53,620 --> 00:07:54,649
I only saw her back.

187
00:07:54,650 --> 00:07:55,780
I can't be certain.

188
00:07:57,770 --> 00:07:58,580
Eunuch Xu.

189
00:07:58,770 --> 00:08:02,220
Take the Imperial Guards
and search every corner of Xiaoyao Pavilion.

190
00:08:02,330 --> 00:08:03,580
Yan Qiu may be here.

191
00:08:03,820 --> 00:08:04,530
Yes, Your Majesty.

192
00:08:08,020 --> 00:08:08,730
Your Majesty.

193
00:08:09,850 --> 00:08:10,580
Official Gu.

194
00:08:10,730 --> 00:08:12,819
Hearing about today's celebration,

195
00:08:12,820 --> 00:08:15,290
I had a golden lock crafted

196
00:08:15,380 --> 00:08:16,530
as a small gift.

197
00:08:17,620 --> 00:08:19,050
You're too kind, Official Li.

198
00:08:19,210 --> 00:08:20,619
Your private room is ready.

199
00:08:20,620 --> 00:08:23,059
As soon as everyone is seated,
we'll serve the dishes.

200
00:08:23,060 --> 00:08:23,900
This way.

201
00:08:25,850 --> 00:08:26,610
Your Majesty.

202
00:08:26,850 --> 00:08:27,939
Congratulations!

203
00:08:27,940 --> 00:08:28,579
Congratulations!

204
00:08:28,580 --> 00:08:29,380
Official Qian.

205
00:08:29,700 --> 00:08:31,050
- Official Xi. Please.
- Congratulations!

206
00:08:32,040 --> 00:08:35,859
(Xiaoyao Pavilion)

207
00:08:35,860 --> 00:08:36,540
Well?

208
00:08:37,050 --> 00:08:38,130
Any leads?

209
00:08:38,140 --> 00:08:40,580
Today's promotion is pretty generous.

210
00:08:40,740 --> 00:08:43,250
Sales are several times higher
than usual.

211
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:44,220
But

212
00:08:44,260 --> 00:08:46,929
if someone's buying in batches

213
00:08:46,930 --> 00:08:48,540
and splitting up their orders,

214
00:08:49,220 --> 00:08:50,610
it'll be hard

215
00:08:50,770 --> 00:08:52,300
to track them down.

216
00:09:02,860 --> 00:09:03,820
Your Majesty!

217
00:09:03,860 --> 00:09:06,370
- Someone! Fetch the Imperial Physician!
- Your Majesty!

218
00:09:06,370 --> 00:09:07,649
- Fetch the Imperial Physician!
- Your Majesty!

219
00:09:07,650 --> 00:09:08,460
Gu Bei!

220
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:09,220
Gu Bei!

221
00:09:09,620 --> 00:09:10,379
Your Majesty!

222
00:09:10,380 --> 00:09:11,250
Your Majesty!

223
00:09:11,980 --> 00:09:12,820
Your Majesty!

224
00:09:13,740 --> 00:09:15,579
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

225
00:09:15,580 --> 00:09:17,979
♪Our spirit soars to the skies♪

226
00:09:17,980 --> 00:09:23,419
♪The brainy emperor plots the strategy♪

227
00:09:23,420 --> 00:09:27,779
♪The slacker general leads the charge♪

228
00:09:27,780 --> 00:09:30,179
♪Swords clash and warhorses thunder♪

229
00:09:30,180 --> 00:09:32,739
♪Let the history judge our deeds♪

230
00:09:32,740 --> 00:09:38,419
♪Our brotherhood is priceless♪

231
00:09:38,420 --> 00:09:43,980
♪Peace across the land, carefree at last♪

232
00:09:48,260 --> 00:09:50,300
♪Funny moments never stop♪

233
00:09:50,940 --> 00:09:53,140
♪Silly blunders never cease♪

234
00:09:53,340 --> 00:09:57,499
♪Yet through every up and down♪

235
00:09:57,500 --> 00:09:59,460
♪We create miracles♪

236
00:09:59,780 --> 00:10:02,220
♪From naive youths♪

237
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:04,979
♪To legendary heroes♪

238
00:10:04,980 --> 00:10:06,899
♪This journey♪

239
00:10:06,900 --> 00:10:10,939
♪Is one we'll be proud of♪

240
00:10:10,940 --> 00:10:13,460
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

241
00:10:15,940 --> 00:10:18,820
♪Let's create♪

242
00:10:20,860 --> 00:10:28,780
♪A legend of our own♪

